eamwork record is not documented. The other candidates each have a more serious gap in either reliability, technical skill, or crew interaction.\n**Do any of you have information about Candidate\u202fC\u2019s technical competence (e.g., weather assessment or systems knowledge) or Candidate\u202fD\u2019s communication/crew\u2011cooperation strengths?** Those details could shift the balance.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
